  %body
    .flash.js-flash.bg-purple.color-white.l-centered.l-hidden
      %strong.js-flash-text.opacity-0
        Your inquiry submitted successfully! Thanks for your interest in trying out WEVO. We'll
        be reaching out to you shortly, so stay tuned!

    %header
      .wrap
        .logo-wrapper
          .logo
        %a.hide{ href: 'http://www.highstartgroup.com/about-us/', target: '_blank' } About HSG

    %section.hero.bg-khaki
      .wrap
        .wrap-medium.bg-transparent.l-centered
          %h1.mbs Better Products. Faster.
          %h2.subheader.mbs
            Decide with confidence which features and benefits will appeal to your target customers.
          %button.button.button--purple.js-sign-up-button Sign Up
          %span.or or
          %button.button.button--purple.js-learn-more-button Learn More

    %section.js-learn-more-section
      .wrap
        %h2.mbs How WEVO Works
        .wrap-medium
          %p.l-centered.mbm
            WEVO uses state of the art market research science to help you decide which features
            and benefits appeal to your target customers.

      .wrap
        %article
          %i.fa.fa-lightbulb-o.fa-2x
          %h3.header-divider Describe
          %p
            %strong First,
            tell us about the product you want to build, describe who it's for, and which
            features you would like to test.

        %article
          %i.fa.fa-group.fa-2x
          %h3.header-divider Market Test
          %p
            %strong Next, 
            we identify your target customers, from among our community of 4,000,000 people. We enable them to preview your product, and pinpoint the features and benefits they value most. 
        %article
          %i.fa.fa-check-square-o.fa-2x
          %h3.header-divider Select
          %p
            %strong Finally,
            you get a set of actionable recommendations that help you create better
            products, with confidence.

    %section.border-green
      .wrap.mts
        %p.subheader.color-green.mbm
          WEVO uses proven market research science to deliver actionable insights.

      .wrap.mbs
        %article
          %i.fa.fa-lightbulb-o.fa-2x.color-green
          %h3.header-divider.header-green Collective Intelligence
          %p
            WEVO brings together your knowledge, our expertise, and input from your target market,
            to help you validate and quantify the appeal of potential and benefits. So that you can
            prioritize with confidence.

        %article
          %i.fa.fa-flask.fa-2x.color-green
          %h3.header-divider.header-green Proven Science
          %p
            WEVO is powered by state of the art market research science, proven over years of client
            projects. So that you get sound answers, every time!

        %article
          %i.fa.fa-signal.fa-2x.color-green
          %h3.header-divider.header-green Actionable Insights
          %p
            WEVO delivers quantified, actionable insights that you can use immediately. With
            confidence.

    %section.border-purple
      .wrap.mts
        %p.subheader.color-purple.mbm
          WEVO makes it fast and easy to get market input.

      .wrap.mbs
        %article
          %i.fa.fa-flash.fa-2x.color-purple
          %h3.header-divider.header-purple Quick turnaround
          %p Get actionable insights to improve your product in a week.

        %article
          %i.fa.fa-cogs.fa-2x.color-purple
          %h3.header-divider.header-purple Minimal setup
          %p Answer a few simple questions, and let us take it from there.

        %article
          %i.fa.fa-bullseye.fa-2x.color-purple
          %h3.header-divider.header-purple Easy market reach
          %p
            We get input from only people in your target market. Whether it is small business
            owners or busy parents, our panel of 4,000,000 respondents covers everyone.


    %section.bg-khaki
      .wrap
        .wrap-medium
          %h2.mbs The HSG Experience
          %p.l-centered.mbs
            WEVO uses insights and experience from projects with a variety of clients &mdash; startups to
            fortune 100 companies &mdash; to help you create better products.

